{
  "_readme": "v16 representation-complete mixed-player-count control. Uses the same engine-choice action surface, 187-feature engine state, player-count curriculum, seeds, fields, and 500-Elo warm start as the outcome treatment, but multiplayer strategic outcome coefficient is zero.",
